Symbol.Script_3D:
! Base Mounted Pump
IF gs_detlevel_3D_m = -1 THEN gs_detlevel_3D_m = 2 ! Detailed IF gs_detlevel_3D = `Откл.` THEN gs_detlevel_3D_m = 0 IF gs_detlevel_3D = `Простой` THEN gs_detlevel_3D_m = 1 ENDIF
IF gs_detlevel_3D_m = 0 THEN END
res = 24 ! Detailed IF gs_detlevel_3D_m = 1 THEN res = 8 ! Simple
IF useSysMat THEN MainBoxMaterial = sMat MATERIAL MainBoxMaterial PEN gs_cont_pen RESOL res
! --- object --- !
unID = 1 HOTSPOT 0, 0, 0, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT A, 0, 0, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT 0, B, 0, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT A, B, 0, unID: unID=unID+1
IF gs_detlevel_3D_m = 2 THEN
BLOCK A, B, bz ! base
ADD A/2-MIN(2*hdr, A-0.05)/2, B-0.37*B-0.03, bz BLOCK MIN(MAX(2*hdr, 0.015), A-0.05), 0.35*B, bbz*(hdr<0.25)+(ConPosZ_1-0.25-0.1)*(hdr>=0.25) ! base under the back cylind DEL 1
ADD A/2, ConPosY_1+5*B/10, bz ROTx 90 EXTRUDE 5, 0, 0, B/10, 16+32, -ConWidth_1/2, 0, 0, -ConWidth_1/2, ConPosZ_1+ConWidth_1/2-bz+0.02, 0, ConWidth_1/2, ConPosZ_1+ConWidth_1/2-bz+0.02, 0, ConWidth_1/2, 0, 0, -ConWidth_1/2, 0, -1 DEL 2
GROUP "1"
ADD A/2, B-0.39*B-0.03, bz+bbz+hdr ROTx -90 CYLIND 0.39*B, MIN(MAX(hdr, 0.03), 0.25) ! back cylind DEL 1 DEL 1
ADD A/2, ConPosY_1, bz+bbz+hdr ROTx -90 CYLIND 0.03, ConWidth_1 DEL 1 DEL 1
ADD A/2, ConPosY_1+0.03, bz+bbz+hdr ROTx -90 CYLIND ConPosY_2+ConWidth_2/2-ConPosY_1, hdr+0.03 ! engine 1 DEL 1 DEL 1
ADD A/2, ConPosY_1+0.03+B/10, bz+bbz+hdr ROTx -90 CONE B/10, 0.9*hdr, 0.6*hdr, 90, 90 ! engine 2 DEL 1 DEL 1
ADD A/2, ConPosY_1+0.03+B/10+B/10, bz+bbz+hdr ROTx -90 CONE B/8, 0.5*hdr, 0.35*hdr, 90, 90 ! engine 3 DEL 1 DEL 1
ADD A/2, ConPosY_1+B/10+B/10+2*B/10, bz+bbz+hdr ROTx -90 CYLIND B/10, ConWidth_1/2 DEL 1 DEL 1
ENDGROUP
GROUP "2"
ADD A/2, 0.03, bz+bbz+hdr ROTx -90 CYLIND B-0.03, ConWidth_1/3 ! arbor DEL 1 DEL 1
ADD ConPosX_2, ConPosY_2, ConPosZ_1 CYLIND ConPosZ_2-ConPosZ_1, ConWidth_2/2 DEL 1
! ADD ConPosX_2, ConPosY_2, ConPosZ_2-0.021 ! CYLIND 0.02, ConWidth_2 ! DEL 1
ADD A/2-2*hdr/3, ConPosY_1+0.03+(ConPosY_2+ConWidth_2/2-ConPosY_1)/4, bz BLOCK 4*hdr/3, (ConPosY_2+ConWidth_2/2-ConPosY_1)/2, ConPosZ_1-hdr-bz ! base under the back cylind DEL 1
ENDGROUP
result_01=ADDGROUP ("1", "2") PLACEGROUP result_01
KILLGROUP "1" KILLGROUP "2" KILLGROUP result_01
ELSE
BLOCK A, B, bz ! base
ADD A/2-MIN(2*hdr, A-0.05)/2, B-0.37*B-0.03, bz BLOCK MIN(2*hdr, A-0.05), 0.35*B, bbz*(hdr<0.25)+(ConPosZ_1-0.25-0.1)*(hdr>=0.25) ! base under the back cylind DEL 1
GROUP "3"
ADD A/2, B-0.39*B-0.03, bz+bbz+hdr ROTx -90 CYLIND 0.39*B, MIN(hdr, 0.25) ! back cylind DEL 1 DEL 1
ADD A/2, ConPosY_1, bz+bbz+hdr ROTx -90 CYLIND 0.03, ConWidth_1 DEL 1 DEL 1
ADD A/2, ConPosY_1+0.03, bz+bbz+hdr ROTx -90 CYLIND ConPosY_2+ConWidth_2/2-ConPosY_1, hdr+0.03 ! engine 1 DEL 1 DEL 1
ADD A/2, ConPosY_1+0.03+B/10, bz+bbz+hdr ROTx -90 CONE B/10+B/8, 0.9*hdr, 0.35*hdr, 90, 90 ! engine 2 DEL 1 DEL 1
ENDGROUP
GROUP "4"
ADD A/2, 0.03, bz+bbz+hdr ROTx -90 CYLIND B-0.03, ConWidth_1/3 ! arbor DEL 1 DEL 1
ADD ConPosX_2, ConPosY_2, ConPosZ_1 CYLIND ConPosZ_2-ConPosZ_1, ConWidth_2/2 DEL 1
ADD A/2-2*hdr/3, ConPosY_1+0.03+(ConPosY_2+ConWidth_2/2-ConPosY_1)/4, bz BLOCK 4*hdr/3, (ConPosY_2+ConWidth_2/2-ConPosY_1)/2, ConPosZ_1-hdr-bz ! base under the back cylind DEL 1
ENDGROUP
result_02=ADDGROUP ("3", "4") PLACEGROUP result_02
KILLGROUP "3" KILLGROUP "4" KILLGROUP result_02
ENDIF
!--- CONNECTIONS --- !
CALL "MEP_m_ConnectionsMEP_4" PARAMETERS SetProgram = SetProgram, ui_current_con = ui_current_con, MEP_NumberConnections = MEP_NumberConnections, MEP_NumConnectionData = gs_Connections, gs_AddConnections = gs_AddConnections, cShow3D = 1, gs_ConMat = MainBoxMaterial, MEP_InsShow = 0, MEP_cline_show_3D = 0, gs_cont_pen = gs_cont_pen, ConPosX_1=ConPosX_1, ConPosY_1=ConPosY_1, ConPosZ_1=ConPosZ_1, ConLength_1=ConLength_1, ConEdit_1 = 14, ConPosX_2=ConPosX_2, ConPosY_2=ConPosY_2, ConPosZ_2=ConPosZ_2, ConLength_2=ConLength_2, ConEdit_2 = 14 END
Symbol.Script_2D:
! Base Mounted Pump
PEN gs_cont_pen SET FILL gs_fill_type
unID = 1 DrawingNum = 1 IF DrawingNum = 1 THEN ! Top
! --- MAIN BOX --- !
HOTSPOT2 0, 0, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 A, 0, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 A, B, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 0, B, unID: unID=unID+1
POLY2_B 4, 1+2+4+64, gs_fill_pen, gs_back_pen, 0, 0, 1, A, 0, 1, A, B, 1, 0, B, 1
ADD2 A/2-(hdr+0.03), ConPosY_1+0.03 POLY2_B 4, 1+2+4+64, gs_fill_pen, gs_back_pen, 0, 0, 1, 2*(hdr+0.03), 0, 1, 2*(hdr+0.03), ConPosY_2+ConWidth_2/2-ConPosY_1, 1, 0, ConPosY_2+ConWidth_2/2-ConPosY_1, 1 DEL 1
ADD2 A/2-ConWidth_1/3, 0.03+(ConPosY_2+ConWidth_2/2)+B/10+B/8 xx = 2*ConWidth_1/3 yy = B-(0.03+(ConPosY_2+ConWidth_2/2)+B/10+B/8)-0.03-0.39*B POLY2_B 4, 1+2+4+64, gs_fill_pen, gs_back_pen, 0, 0, 1, xx, 0, 1, xx, yy, 1, 0, yy, 1 DEL 1
ADD2 A/2-MIN(hdr, 0.25), B-0.39*B-0.03 POLY2_B 4, 1+2+4+64, gs_fill_pen, gs_back_pen, 0, 0, 1, 2*MIN(hdr, 0.25), 0, 1, 2*MIN(hdr, 0.25), 0.39*B, 1, 0, 0.39*B, 1 DEL 1
ADD2 A/2-ConWidth_1/3, B-0.03 xx = 2*ConWidth_1/3 yy = 0.03 POLY2_B 4, 1+2+4+64, gs_fill_pen, gs_back_pen, 0, 0, 1, xx, 0, 1, xx, yy, 1, 0, yy, 1 DEL 1
ADD2 A/2-ConWidth_1, ConPosY_1 xx = 2*ConWidth_1 yy = 0.03 POLY2_B 4, 1+2+4+64, gs_fill_pen, gs_back_pen, 0, 0, 1, xx, 0, 1, xx, yy, 1, 0, yy, 1 DEL 1
ADD2 A/2-(hdr+0.03), ConPosY_1+0.03 xx = 2*(hdr+0.03) yy = ConPosY_2+ConWidth_2/2-ConPosY_1 POLY2_B 4, 1+2+4+64, gs_fill_pen, gs_back_pen, 0, 0, 1, xx, 0, 1, xx, yy, 1, 0, yy, 1 DEL 1
ADD2 A/2, 0 ADD2 -0.9*hdr, 0.03+(ConPosY_2+ConWidth_2/2) POLY2_B 4, 1+2+4+64, gs_fill_pen, gs_back_pen, 0, 0, 1, 0.55*hdr, B/10+B/8, 1, -0.55*hdr+1.8*hdr, B/10+B/8, 1, 1.8*hdr, 0, 1 DEL 2
!! ADD2 A/2-ConWidth_1/2, 0.03+(ConPosY_2+ConWidth_2/2)+B/10+B/8+B/10-(B/8-B/10) !! RECT2 0, 0, 2*ConWidth_1/2, B/10 !! DEL 1
ENDIF
! --- CONNECTIONS --- !
ROT2 -SYMB_ROTANGLE * (DrawingNum > 1 AND NOT(SYMB_MIRRORED))+SYMB_ROTANGLE * (DrawingNum > 1 AND SYMB_MIRRORED)
IF DrawingNum = 2 THEN PROJECT2 -3, 90, 2 ! Bottom IF DrawingNum = 3 THEN PROJECT2 4, 270, 2 ! Front IF DrawingNum = 4 THEN PROJECT2 4, 90, 2 ! Back IF DrawingNum = 5 THEN PROJECT2 4, 180*(SYMB_MIRRORED), 2 ! Right IF DrawingNum = 6 THEN PROJECT2 4, 180*NOT(SYMB_MIRRORED), 2 ! Left
CALL "MEP_m_ConnectionsMEP_4" PARAMETERS SetProgram = SetProgram, ui_current_con = ui_current_con, MEP_NumberConnections = MEP_NumberConnections, MEP_NumConnectionData = gs_Connections, gs_AddConnections = gs_AddConnections, DrawingNum = DrawingNum, MEP_InsShow = 0, MEP_cline_show = 0, gs_cont_pen = gs_cont_pen, gs_fill_type=gs_fill_type, gs_fill_pen=gs_fill_pen, gs_back_pen=gs_back_pen, ConPosX_1=ConPosX_1, ConPosY_1=ConPosY_1, ConLength_1=ConLength_1, ConEdit_1 = 1, ConPosX_2=ConPosX_2, ConPosY_2=ConPosY_2, ConLength_2=ConLength_2, ConEdit_2 = 0 DEL 1
END
Symbol.Script_1D:
! Base Mounted Pump
EPS = 0.0001
edgeThick = 0.00625
! object parameters
bz=0.1 ! alaptest magassága bbz=0.07 ! hátsó henger alatti alap magassága hdr=(ConPosZ_1-bz-bbz) ! hátsó henger sugara

z = 0

Symbol.Script_VL:
! Base Mounted Pump
call "FM_types_MEP" parameters
DIM shape_typ_to_validation[3] shape_typ_to_validation[1] = 0 ! Rectangle shape_typ_to_validation[2] = 1 ! Circle shape_typ_to_validation[3] = 0 ! Oval
IF GLOB_MODPAR_NAME = "gs_detlevel_3D" OR gs_detlevel_3D_m = -1 THEN gs_detlevel_3D_m = 2 ! Detailed IF gs_detlevel_3D = `Откл.` THEN gs_detlevel_3D_m = 0 IF gs_detlevel_3D = `Простой` THEN gs_detlevel_3D_m = 1 PARAMETERS gs_detlevel_3D_m = gs_detlevel_3D_m ELSE IF gs_detlevel_3D_m = 0 THEN gs_detlevel_3D = `Откл.` IF gs_detlevel_3D_m = 1 THEN gs_detlevel_3D = `Простой` IF gs_detlevel_3D_m = 2 THEN gs_detlevel_3D = `Детальный` PARAMETERS gs_detlevel_3D = gs_detlevel_3D ENDIF
VALUES "gs_detlevel_3D" `Детальный`,`Простой`,`Откл.` VALUES "gs_detlevel_3D_m" 2, 1, 0
! --- MAIN PARAMETERS --- !
IF NOT(SetProgram) THEN IF A<0.25 THEN A =0.25 PARAMETERS A =0.25 ENDIF IF B<0.60 THEN B=0.60 PARAMETERS B=0.60 ENDIF VALUES "A" RANGE [0.25,] VALUES "B" RANGE [0.60,] ENDIF

ConWVecX = -1 ConWVecY = 0 ConWVecZ = 0
IF NOT(SetProgram) THEN VALUES "ConWidth_1" RANGE [0.02, A/2] PARAMETERS ConDepth_1 = ConWidth_1 HIDEPARAMETER "ConDepth_1"
PARAMETERS ConPosX_1 = A/2 PARAMETERS ConPosY_1 = 0 VALUES "ConPosZ_1" RANGE [A/2, A+bz] ENDIF

ConNominalWidth = ConNominalWidth_1, ConNominalDepth = ConNominalDepth_1, ConWidth = ConWidth_1, ConDepth = ConDepth_1, ConLength = ConLength_1, ConWallThickness = ConWallThickness_1, ConConnectorWidth = ConConnectorWidth_1, ConConnectorDepth = ConConnectorDepth_1, ConConnectorWidth2 = ConConnectorWidth2_1, ConToolType = ConToolType_1, ConStatus = ConStatus_1, ConType_1 = ConType_1, ConConnectorType_1 = ConConnectorType_1, ConSystem_1 = ConSystem_1, ui_page_idx = ui_page_idx, ui_current_con = ui_current_con, shape_typ_to_validation = shape_typ_to_validation, MEP_enabled_geometry_mod = 1, bUIConnectionStatusCheckbox = 1
PARAMETERS MEP_ConInfo[ConID][1] = STR(ConToolType_1, 1, 0) PARAMETERS MEP_ConInfo[ConID][2] = ConName PARAMETERS MEP_ConInfo[ConID][3] = "0"
! --- 2nd CONNECTION --- !
ConID = 2 ConName = `Труба Выпускного Соединения`
ConDVecX = 0 ConDVecY = 0 ConDVecZ = 1
ConWVecX = -1 ConWVecY = 0 ConWVecZ = 0
IF NOT(SetProgram) THEN IF ConWidth_2 < 0.02 THEN ConWidth_2 = 0.02 IF ConWidth_2 > A/4 THEN ConWidth_2 = A/4 VALUES "ConWidth_2" RANGE [0.02, A/4] PARAMETERS ConDepth_2 = ConWidth_2 HIDEPARAMETER "ConDepth_2"
PARAMETERS ConPosX_2 = A/2+hdr+0.03-ConWidth_2/2 PARAMETERS ConPosY_2 = ConPosY_1+ConWidth_2/2+0.03 VALUES "ConPosZ_2" RANGE [ConPosZ_1+hdr+0.03, ] ENDIF
CALL "MEP_m_ConnectionsMEP_4" PARAMETERS SetProgram = SetProgram, gs_Connections = gs_Connections, MEP_NumConnectionData = MEP_NumConnectionData, MEP_StrConnectionData = MEP_StrConnectionData, MEP_NumberConnections = MEP_NumberConnections, gs_AddConnections = gs_AddConnections, ConName = ConName, ConID = ConID, ConPosX = ConPosX_2, ConPosY = ConPosY_2, ConPosZ = ConPosZ_2, ConDVecX = ConDVecX, ConDVecY = ConDVecY, ConDVecZ = ConDVecZ, ConWVecX = ConWVecX, ConWVecY = ConWVecY, ConWVecZ = ConWVecZ,
ConNominalWidth = ConNominalWidth_2, ConNominalDepth = ConNominalDepth_2, ConWidth = ConWidth_2, ConDepth = ConDepth_2, ConLength = ConLength_2, ConWallThickness = ConWallThickness_2, ConConnectorWidth = ConConnectorWidth_2, ConConnectorDepth = ConConnectorDepth_2, ConConnectorWidth2 = ConConnectorWidth2_2, ConToolType = ConToolType_2, ConStatus = ConStatus_2, ConType_2 = ConType_2, ConConnectorType_2 = ConConnectorType_2, ConSystem_2 = ConSystem_2, shape_typ_to_validation = shape_typ_to_validation, MEP_enabled_geometry_mod = 1, bUIConnectionStatusCheckbox = 1
PARAMETERS MEP_ConInfo[ConID][1] = STR(ConToolType_2, 1, 0) PARAMETERS MEP_ConInfo[ConID][2] = ConName PARAMETERS MEP_ConInfo[ConID][3] = "0"
IF setProgram THEN SetProgram = 0 PARAMETERS SetProgram = SetProgram ENDIF
